Ireland’s Kenny Says Will Be No Blanket Writedown of Home Loans

-- B y   D a r a   D o y l e
-- 
2011-10-11T15:21:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/ireland-s-kenny-says-will-be-no-blanket-writedown-of-home-loans.html
Irish Prime Minister  Enda Kenny  said
any new proposals on mortgage arrears need to distingusih
between those “who can’t pay and those who won’t pay.”  In parliament in Dublin today, he said that a report on
arrears will be published tomorrow.  He said there will be no
“blanket” write-down of mortgage debt.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
